### M38: Login (real auth)
POST http://localhost:3100/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "ChangeMe123!"
}

### M38: Authenticated default route
GET http://localhost:3100/

### M38: Protected page redirects to login when unauthenticated
GET http://localhost:3100/pos

### M38: Not authorized page (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3100/not-authorized?required=ADMIN

### M38: Logout
POST http://localhost:3100/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}
